    'services.mobile.content': 'We develop mobile applications for iOS and Android platforms - from simple utility apps to complex business solutions with backend integration. Over 6 years of experience and 47+ successfully completed projects. Mobile app development in Kazakhstan is our specialty. We work with clients throughout Kazakhstan, creating mobile solutions that help businesses reach their customers on mobile devices.\n\nOur services include:\n\nNative iOS Apps\nNative iOS applications developed with Swift and SwiftUI. Full integration with iOS features, App Store optimization, and modern iOS design guidelines. Perfect performance and native user experience.\n\nNative Android Apps\nNative Android applications developed with Kotlin and Jetpack Compose. Material Design guidelines, Google Play optimization, and integration with Android services.\n\nCross-Platform Apps\nCross-platform mobile applications using React Native or Flutter. Single codebase for iOS and Android, faster development, cost-effective solution. Perfect for startups and businesses that need apps for both platforms.\n\nHybrid Apps\nHybrid mobile applications using web technologies (React, Vue) wrapped in native containers. Cost-effective solution for simple to medium complexity apps.\n\nApp Maintenance and Updates\nOngoing mobile app maintenance: updates, bug fixes, new feature additions, performance optimization, and App Store/Google Play submissions.\n\nAll mobile apps are created with:\n- Native or cross-platform technologies (Swift, Kotlin, React Native, Flutter)\n- Modern UI/UX design\n- Backend integration and API connections\n- Push notifications\n- App Store and Google Play optimization\n- Security and performance optimization',
