    'services.mobile.examples': 'Examples of completed mobile app projects:\n\n- Na\'Vi Connect - Mobile app for event management\n- Business utility apps for internal processes\n- E-commerce mobile applications',
    'services.mobile.faq.0.question': 'How long does it take to develop a mobile app?',
    'services.mobile.faq.0.answer': 'Development time depends on complexity. A simple app takes 1-2 months, a medium complexity app - 2-4 months, a complex app with backend - 4-6 months. Cross-platform apps can be developed faster.',
    'services.mobile.faq.1.question': 'Which platform should We choose: iOS, Android, or both?',
    'services.mobile.faq.1.answer': 'We recommend starting with the platform where your target audience is most active. For Kazakhstan, Android has a larger market share, but iOS users often have higher purchasing power. Cross-platform development allows creating apps for both platforms simultaneously.',
    'services.mobile.faq.2.question': 'What technologies do you use?',
    'services.mobile.faq.2.answer': 'We use native technologies (Swift for iOS, Kotlin for Android) and cross-platform frameworks (React Native, Flutter). We choose the best technology based on project requirements, budget, and timeline.',
    'services.mobile.faq.3.question': 'Do you help with App Store and Google Play submission?',
    'services.mobile.faq.3.answer': 'Yes, we help with app submission to App Store and Google Play, including preparing screenshots, descriptions, keywords, and handling the review process.',
    'services.mobile.faq.4.question': 'Can you integrate the app with existing backend?',
    'services.mobile.faq.4.answer': 'Yes, we can integrate mobile apps with existing backends, APIs, and third-party services. We work with REST APIs, GraphQL, and various authentication systems.',
    'services.mobile.faq.5.question': 'How much does mobile app development cost?',
    'services.mobile.faq.5.answer': 'The cost depends on complexity. A simple app starts from 500,000 ₸, a medium complexity app - from 1,000,000 ₸, a complex app - from 1,500,000 ₸. Cross-platform apps are more cost-effective than developing separate native apps.',
    'services.mobile.faq.6.question': 'Do you provide app maintenance?',
    'services.mobile.faq.6.answer': 'Yes, we provide ongoing app maintenance: updates, bug fixes, new features, performance optimization, and App Store/Google Play updates. Flexible maintenance packages depending on your needs.',
    
