    'services.mobile.cards.0.extended': 'We develop native iOS applications for businesses in Almaty, Astana, Shymkent and throughout Kazakhstan. Swift and SwiftUWe development, full iOS feature integration, App Store optimization, modern iOS design guidelines. Perfect performance and native user experience. Working with businesses throughout Kazakhstan.',
    
