    // Design service
    'services.design.h1': 'UI/UX Design | Web Design, Mobile App Design, Website Redesign',
    'services.design.intro': 'Professional UI/UX design services in Almaty, Astana, Shymkent and throughout Kazakhstan. We create modern, intuitive interfaces that improve user experience and increase conversions.',
    'services.design.content': 'We provide UI/UX design services for websites, mobile applications, and digital products. Over 6 years of experience and 47+ successfully completed projects. Design in Kazakhstan is our specialty. We work with clients throughout Kazakhstan, creating user-centered designs that combine aesthetics with functionality.\n\nOur services include:\n\nLanding Page Design\nModern, conversion-optimized designs for landing pages. Mobile-first approach, clear call-to-action, intuitive navigation. Perfect for marketing campaigns and product launches.\n\nWebsite Design\nComprehensive design for multi-page websites: corporate sites, portfolios, business websites. Design system, style guide, interactive prototypes. User experience optimization and modern aesthetics.\n\nMobile App Design\nUI/UX design for iOS and Android applications. User flow design, interface design, iconography, animations. Design system and component library for consistent user experience.\n\nWebsite Redesign\nModernization of existing websites: new design, improved UX, updated visual style. Analysis of current design, user research, and implementation of best practices.\n\nDesign System and Guidelines\nCreation of comprehensive design systems: component libraries, style guides, design tokens. Ensures consistency across all platforms and simplifies future development.\n\nAll designs are created with:\n- User-centered design approach\n- Modern design tools (Figma, Adobe XD)\n- Responsive and adaptive design\n- Accessibility standards (WCAG)\n- Design system and component library',
    'services.design.process': 'My design process:\n\n1. Research and analysis of requirements\n2. User research and competitor analysis\n3. Wireframing and information architecture\n4. Visual design and prototyping\n5. User testing and iteration\n6. Design system creation\n7. Handoff to development team',
    'services.design.examples': 'Examples of completed design projects:\n\n- Landing page design for e-commerce\n- Corporate website redesign\n- Mobile app UI/UX design\n- Design system for SaaS platform',
    'services.design.faq.0.question': 'How long does it take to create a design?',
    'services.design.faq.0.answer': 'Design time depends on complexity. A landing page design takes 1-2 weeks, a multi-page website design - 2-4 weeks, a mobile app design - 3-5 weeks.',
    'services.design.faq.1.question': 'What design tools do you use?',
    'services.design.faq.1.answer': 'We work with modern design tools: Figma, Adobe XD, Sketch. We create interactive prototypes, design systems, and provide all source files for development.',
    'services.design.faq.2.question': 'Do you provide design revisions?',
    'services.design.faq.2.answer': 'Yes, all design projects include revision rounds. The number of revisions depends on the project scope and is discussed before starting work.',
    'services.design.faq.3.question': 'Can you work with existing brand guidelines?',
    'services.design.faq.3.answer': 'Yes, we can work with existing brand guidelines, color palettes, and style guides. We ensure consistency with your brand identity while improving user experience.',
    'services.design.faq.4.question': 'Do you create responsive designs?',
    'services.design.faq.4.answer': 'Yes, all our designs are responsive and adaptive. We design for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices, ensuring optimal user experience on all screen sizes.',
    'services.design.faq.5.question': 'What files do you provide?',
    'services.design.faq.5.answer': 'We provide all necessary files: Figma/XD source files, exported assets (images, icons), style guides, and design specifications for developers.',
    'services.design.faq.6.question': 'How much does design cost?',
    'services.design.faq.6.answer': 'The cost depends on complexity. Landing page design starts from 80,000 ₸, multi-page website design - from 200,000 ₸, mobile app design - from 250,000 ₸. We provide detailed estimates after discussing your requirements.',
    
