    // Consulting service
    'services.consulting.h1': 'Development Consulting and Training | Technology Consultations, Programming Training',
    'services.consulting.intro': 'Professional development consulting and programming training services in Almaty, Astana, Shymkent and throughout Kazakhstan. We provide technology consultations, code review, and team training to help businesses succeed.',
    'services.consulting.content': 'We provide development consulting and programming training services for businesses and teams. Over 6 years of experience and 47+ successfully completed projects. Consulting in Kazakhstan is our specialty. We work with clients throughout Kazakhstan, helping them make informed technology decisions, improve code quality, and develop their teams.\n\nOur services include:\n\nTechnology Consultations\nConsultations on technology stack selection, architecture decisions, and best practices. Help choosing the right tools, frameworks, and approaches for your project. Analysis of existing solutions and recommendations for improvement.\n\nCode Review\nComprehensive code review services: code quality analysis, security audit, performance optimization, best practices compliance. Detailed feedback and recommendations for improvement.\n\nTeam Training\nProgramming and development training for teams: React, Next.js, TypeScript, Node.js, and other technologies. Custom training programs tailored to your team\'s needs and skill levels.\n\nProject Architecture Consulting\nConsultations on project architecture, system design, and scalability. Help designing scalable, maintainable, and efficient solutions. Technology stack recommendations and implementation strategies.\n\nTechnical Support and Mentoring\nOngoing technical support and mentoring for development teams. Code review, architecture guidance, problem-solving assistance, and knowledge sharing.\n\nAll consulting services include:\n- Personalized approach to each client\n- Practical experience and real-world examples\n- Modern technologies and best practices\n- Detailed documentation and recommendations\n- Flexible scheduling and remote options',
    'services.consulting.process': 'My consulting process:\n\n1. Initial consultation and needs assessment\n2. Analysis of current situation and requirements\n3. Development of recommendations and action plan\n4. Implementation support and guidance\n5. Follow-up and continuous improvement',
    'services.consulting.examples': 'Examples of consulting services:\n\n- Technology stack selection for startup\n- Code review and optimization for existing project\n- Team training on React and Next.js\n- Architecture consulting for SaaS platform',
    'services.consulting.faq.0.question': 'How long does a consultation session take?',
    'services.consulting.faq.0.answer': 'Consultation sessions typically last 1-2 hours. The duration depends on the complexity of the topic and your specific needs. We can adjust the schedule to fit your requirements.',
    'services.consulting.faq.1.question': 'Do you provide remote consultations?',
    'services.consulting.faq.1.answer': 'Yes, we provide both in-person and remote consultations. Remote consultations are conducted via video calls, which allows me to work with clients throughout Kazakhstan and beyond.',
    'services.consulting.faq.2.question': 'What technologies do you consult on?',
    'services.consulting.faq.2.answer': 'We consult on modern web development technologies: React, Next.js, TypeScript, Node.js, PostgreSQL, MongoDB, and related tools. We also provide guidance on architecture, best practices, and development workflows.',
    'services.consulting.faq.3.question': 'Can you review code from any technology stack?',
    'services.consulting.faq.3.answer': 'We specialize in JavaScript/TypeScript ecosystems (React, Next.js, Node.js), but We can also review code in other languages and provide general recommendations on code quality, architecture, and best practices.',
    'services.consulting.faq.4.question': 'How much does consulting cost?',
    'services.consulting.faq.4.answer': 'Consultation rates start from 10,000 ₸ per hour. Code review starts from 50,000 ₸, team training - from 200,000 ₸. We provide detailed estimates based on your specific needs and project scope.',
    'services.consulting.faq.5.question': 'Do you provide training materials?',
    'services.consulting.faq.5.answer': 'Yes, we provide training materials, documentation, code examples, and practical exercises. All materials are tailored to your team\'s needs and skill levels.',
    'services.consulting.faq.6.question': 'Can you help with project architecture?',
    'services.consulting.faq.6.answer': 'Yes, we provide architecture consulting services. We help design scalable, maintainable systems, choose appropriate technologies, and plan implementation strategies.',
    
